{"tid":1328691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勿中伏] 唔好糾纏喺張超雄陳同佳度，要聚焦返去五大訴求度！","createTime":"2019-07-18T03:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T06:49:01.000Z","uid":270506,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6f327226bece3516955057fd18f31d98a615f028","tid":1328691,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:56:20.000Z","msg":"大家有冇諗到尋晚突然爆左張超雄單野其實本身就係一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">帶風向嘅局</span></strong>？<br />\n當大家熱烈討論張超雄嘅草案或者陳同佳單野點拆，忘記五大訴求，淨係斟酌於小處，西環同林鄭在偷笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位手足要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">認定五大訴求呢個主幹</span></span></strong>，分清主次，對呢啲旁枝末節不必過度深入討論，否則就會中咗模糊焦點之計！<br />\n<br />\n集中火力重申五大訴求：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span>"},{"pid":"43b0ad2639ce06016117fc4f2c29e219babe3035","tid":1328691,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6e85bbbc2c9c7d5fa54195a45d2608225b4208","tid":1328691,"uid":17796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:58:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d32ef4d9321ecda24400a7143553f565081be64b","tid":1328691,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:58:19.000Z","msg":"[7.21 遊行] 好撚重要 必需置頂!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327475</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5cf00bfc1f94480865ebafcbcb75788dcd802bbd","tid":1328691,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:58:35.000Z","msg":"[正視聽]張昭雄方案絕不能接受 楊岳橋及尹兆堅方案亦應暫緩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/RCOiRU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/RCOiRU</a>"},{"pid":"ff87c7c0784b5596c1f7d91ce748c07c5